<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[5] =E2=80=9CMarket,=E2=80=9D as an adjective,=
 is how this is ordinarily expressed by financiers and lawyers, though jour=
nalists=E2=80=99 editors don=E2=80=99t like it.</p>
